《'''反了'''》<ref name="專輯介紹">{{cite web |url=http://www.books.com.tw/products/0020191326 |title=反了專輯介紹 - 蕾哈娜 |accessdate=2017-02-24 |work= |publisher=[[博客來|博客來]] |date= |archive-date=2017-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301011602/http://www.books.com.tw/products/0020191326 |dead-url=no }}</ref>（{{lang-en|''Anti''}}）是[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]歌手[[蕾哈娜|蕾哈娜]]的第八張錄音室專輯，於2016年1月28日通過[[Tidal|Tidal]]發行免費數字下載，並於翌日29日正式發行。專輯至今發行了四支單曲，包括獲得[[美國|美國]][[告示牌百強單曲榜|告示牌百強單曲榜]]九周冠軍的《[[加把勁_(蕾哈娜歌曲)|加把勁]]》，以及前十單曲《[[需要我|需要我]]》、《[[無法忘懷的愛|無法忘懷的愛]]》等。專輯以約166,000張的銷售單位登上美國[[告示牌二百強專輯榜|告示牌二百強專輯榜]]位置，成為其第二張美國冠軍專輯<ref name="antitops">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6867227/rihanna-anti-billboard-200-no-1|title=Rihanna's 'Anti' Rules at No. 1 on Billboard 200 Albums Chart|work=Billboard|last=Caulfield|first=Keith|date=2016-02-07|accessdate=2016-02-08|archive-date=2016-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160711035240/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6867227/rihanna-anti-billboard-200-no-1|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於發行兩天後因[[三星集团|三星]]先行購買了100萬張專輯供用戶免費下載而獲[[美國唱片業協會|美國唱片業協會]]認證為白金唱片<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.complex.com/music/2016/01/rihanna-anti-album-already-platinum | title=Rihanna's 'ANTI' Album Is Already Platinum | work=Complex | date=2016-01-29 | accessdate=2017-01-28 | archive-date=2016-02-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160205185247/http://www.complex.com/music/2016/01/rihanna-anti-album-already-platinum | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

專輯獲得樂評家整體正面的評價，並獲入選多個2016年年度最佳專輯排名榜。專輯同時獲提名[[第59届格莱美奖|第59届格莱美奖]]最佳當代城市音樂專輯及最佳唱片包裝<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.billboardradiochina.com/story/2017-ge-lin-mei-jiang-ti-ming-chu-lu-zh_hk | title=2017格林美獎提名出爐 | work=Billboard China | date=2016-12-07 | accessdate=2017-02-28 | archive-date=2017-03-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301010145/http://www.billboardradiochina.com/story/2017-ge-lin-mei-jiang-ti-ming-chu-lu-zh_hk | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 發行背景 ==
2012年發行第七張錄音室專輯《[[道歉太難|道歉太難]]》後，蕾哈娜隨即展開「璀鑽世界巡迴演唱會」世界巡迴演出等一系列宣傳工作<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/the-juice/475226/rihanna-announces-diamonds-world-tour | title=Rihanna Announces 'Diamonds World Tour' | work=Billboard | date=2012-09-07 | accessdate=2017-02-28 | archive-date=2015-11-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106222442/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/the-juice/475226/rihanna-announces-diamonds-world-tour | dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而專輯宣傳期完結後，蕾哈娜並沒有一如以往般投入下一張錄音室專輯的準備工作，反而選擇暫緩處理音樂的工作<ref name=nmeinterview>{{cite web|title=NME interview|url=http://www.nme.com/features/rihanna-exclusive-interview-i-break-the-rules-even-when-i-dont-intend-to|website=NME|accessdate=2015-10-08|archive-date=2015-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151124074340/http://www.nme.com/features/rihanna-exclusive-interview-i-break-the-rules-even-when-i-dont-intend-to|dead-url=no}}</ref>。期間她參與了動畫電影《[[無敵安樂窩|無敵安樂窩]]》的角色配音，並同時獻聲於原聲帶歌曲<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/the-juice/6509233/rihanna-as-real-as-you-and-me-dancing-in-the-dark-home-soundtrack-stream | title=Listen to Rihanna's Two New Songs From the 'Home' Soundtrack | work=Billboard | date=2015-03-09 | accessdate=2017-02-28 | archive-date=2016-01-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160120074336/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/the-juice/6509233/rihanna-as-real-as-you-and-me-dancing-in-the-dark-home-soundtrack-stream | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年蕾哈娜先後發行了《{{Link-en|FourFiveSeconds|FourFiveSeconds}}》、《{{Link-en|Bitch Better Have My Money|Bitch Better Have My Money}}》及《{{Link-en|American Oxygen|American Oxygen}}》三支單曲，被認為即將攜個人第八張錄音室專輯回歸樂壇<ref>{{cite news | url=https://planetradio.co.uk/aire/entertainment/music/rihanna-finally-shares-politically-charged-american-oxygen-music-video-watch/ | title=Rihanna finally shares her politically-charged ‘American Oxygen’ music video – WATCH | work=Radioaire | date=2015-04-16 | accessdate=2017-02-28 | archive-date=2017-03-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301005608/https://planetradio.co.uk/aire/entertainment/music/rihanna-finally-shares-politically-charged-american-oxygen-music-video-watch/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而專輯的發行日期一直未有落實，甚至傳出因單曲成績未如理想而推遲專輯發行的消息<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.vh1.com/news/42168/reasons-rihannas-album-is-delayed/ | title=Where Have You Been? Here’s Why Rihanna’s Album Is Taking So Long | author=Jasmine Grant | work=VH1 | date=2015-07-29 | accessdate=2017-02-28 | archive-date=2017-03-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301092816/http://www.vh1.com/news/42168/reasons-rihannas-album-is-delayed/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。10月7日，蕾哈娜於美國[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]MAMA畫廊的私人歌迷聚會上公佈了第八張錄音室專輯的名字與封面<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.etonline.com/news/173552_rihanna_unveils_groundbreaking_new_album_art_featuring_childhood_photo_is_it_called_anti/ | title=Rihanna Unveils Groundbreaking New 'Anti' Album Art Featuring Childhood Photo | work=Entertainment News | date=2015-10-07 | accessdate=2017-02-28 | archive-date=2017-02-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170224053833/http://www.etonline.com/news/173552_rihanna_unveils_groundbreaking_new_album_art_featuring_childhood_photo_is_it_called_anti/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。此後專輯即將發行的消息甚囂塵上，不時流傳出各種專輯的發行日期<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.bustle.com/articles/127434-could-rihannas-anti-album-be-released-on-friday-rumors-are-swirling-about-this-swift-release-date | title=Could Rihanna's 'Anti' Album Be Released On Friday? Rumors Are Swirling About This Swift Release Date | work=Bustle | date=2015-12-04 | accessdate=2017-02-28 | archive-date=2017-03-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301005435/https://www.bustle.com/articles/127434-could-rihannas-anti-album-be-released-on-friday-rumors-are-swirling-about-this-swift-release-date | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.breatheheavy.com/rihannas-new-album-anti-could-drop-nov-6/ | title=Rihanna’s New Album ‘ANTi’ Could Drop Nov. 6 | author=Jordan Miller | work=Breatheheavy | date=2015-10-14 | accessdate=2017-02-28 | archive-date=2017-03-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301092704/http://www.breatheheavy.com/rihannas-new-album-anti-could-drop-nov-6/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/rihannas-anti-release-date-new-album-expected-to-drop-black-friday-on-tidal-a6746281.html | title=Rihanna's Anti release date: New album expected to drop Black Friday on Tidal | author=Jack Shepherd | work=Independent | date=2015-11-24 | accessdate=2017-02-28 | archive-date=2017-03-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301011209/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/rihannas-anti-release-date-new-album-expected-to-drop-black-friday-on-tidal-a6746281.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。11月23日，蕾哈娜公佈了「反了世界巡迴演唱會」的場次細節<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.justjared.com/2015/11/23/rihanna-announces-anti-world-tour-for-2016/ |  title=Rihanna Announces 'Anti World Tour' 2016 - Full List of Dates!| work=JustJared| date=2015-11-23 | accessdate=2017-02-28}}</ref>，並認為專輯的發行近在咫尺<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/rihanna-new-album-release-date-singer-drop-anti-christmas-day-1534846 | title=Rihanna new album release date: Singer to drop Anti on Christmas Day? | author=Alicia Adejobi | work=ibtimes | date=2015-12-24 | accessdate=2017-02-28 | archive-date=2016-02-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160204023626/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/rihanna-new-album-release-date-singer-drop-anti-christmas-day-1534846 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年1月27日，蕾哈娜於推特上親自確認新曲《[[加把勁_(蕾哈娜歌曲)|加把勁]]》為專輯首支單曲發行，意味著先前發行的三支單曲皆不收錄於新專輯中。同時專輯所有詳細信息完全解禁，並於翌日透過Tidal提供下載<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.capitalxtra.com/artists/rihanna/news/work-feat-drake-and-twitter-just-went-crazy/#OvKBymVWFlwePY0M.97 | title=Rihanna Just Dropped ‘Work’ Feat. Drake And Twitter Went Crazy | work=Capitalxtra | date=2016-01-27 | accessdate=2017-02-28 | archive-date=2017-03-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301094227/http://www.capitalxtra.com/artists/rihanna/news/work-feat-drake-and-twitter-just-went-crazy/#OvKBymVWFlwePY0M.97 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 標題與封面 ==
2015年10月7日，蕾哈娜在美國洛杉磯的MAMA畫廊舉行了與歌迷的私人見面會，並舉行了開專輯名稱與封面的揭幕儀式。在此前，專輯大多被歌迷及媒體稱為R8，代表蕾哈娜第八張錄音室專輯<ref>{{cite web|title=Rihanna Reveals #R8's REAL Name, #ANTI + Cover Details!|url=http://unartiste.co/rihanna-reveals-r8s-real-name-anti-cover-details/|work=unartiste|accessdate=2015-10-08|archive-date=2017-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301005700/http://unartiste.co/rihanna-reveals-r8s-real-name-anti-cover-details/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。而蕾哈娜則在揭示專輯的封面時同時宣佈專輯的正式名稱為《'''ANTI'''》，其中畫廊的一項展品展出示專輯名稱的意思為「一個反對特定政策、活動或想法的人」<ref>{{cite web|title=Rihanna cover changes history of album art|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2015/oct/08/rihanna-anti-album-cover-changes-history-of-album-art|website=The Guardian|accessdate=2015-10-08|archive-date=2015-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151008221820/http://www.theguardian.com/music/2015/oct/08/rihanna-anti-album-cover-changes-history-of-album-art|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在展出完結後，蕾哈娜在社交媒體上進一步解釋專輯名稱的意義：「透過繼續追隨自己的本能，她致力通過作出與大眾期望對立的事情以產生影響」<ref>{{cite web|title=Rihanna anti cover album art R8|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2015/oct/08/rihanna-anti-album-cover-changes-history-of-album-art|work=The Guardian|accessdate=2015-10-08|archive-date=2015-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151008221820/http://www.theguardian.com/music/2015/oct/08/rihanna-anti-album-cover-changes-history-of-album-art|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

專輯封面由[[以色列|以色列]]藝術家羅伊·納奇負責製作。並被蕾哈娜形容為她最喜歡的專輯封面<ref name="one">{{cite web|title=Rihanna Reveals Album Title & Artwork at Los Angeles|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6721869/rihanna-album-r8-anti-title-artwork-roy-nachum|website=Billboard|access-date=October 8, 2015|archive-date=2021-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210603134202/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6721869/rihanna-album-r8-anti-title-artwork-roy-nachum|dead-url=no}}</ref>。封面特別選用蕾哈娜小時候第一天到幼稚園時所拍攝的照片<ref name="one"/>。封面以黑白色為基調，並漆有紅色的顏料。正中間是拿著黑氣球的小蕾哈娜，一頂金色的皇冠蓋住了她的眼睛<ref name="one"/>。談到封面藝術的概念，納奇說他畫了一個小時候的蕾哈娜，代表她為音樂「帶來新的東西」<ref name=rollingstonecoverart>{{cite web|title=Rihanna's glitzy artsy album cover launch|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/inside-rihannas-glitzy-artsy-album-cover-launch-20151008|work=RollingStone|accessdate=2015-10-08|archive-date=2015-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151009155530/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/inside-rihannas-glitzy-artsy-album-cover-launch-20151008|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

帆布封面上出現詩人洛伊·米切爾所撰寫的詩歌《If They Let Us》，並由封面設計者納奇通過盲文刻錄。蕾哈娜解釋使用盲文寫下詩歌的原因：「有些時候，看得到的人反而是最盲目的人」<ref name="ysolife">{{cite web|title=【Cover Art】蕾哈娜盲目造反？以色列藝術家操刀《Anti》專輯封面|url=https://ysolife.com/cover-art-rihanna-anti/|work=樂手巢|date=2015-10-08|accessdate=2017-02-28|archive-date=2017-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301005753/https://ysolife.com/cover-art-rihanna-anti/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。米切爾在接受《滾石雜誌》訪問時說道：「這首詩在講被誤解時仍然站出來做你認為對的事情。不用符合社會對你的角色設定，你有權做自己的主人。有時候我們會覺得無所適從，因為我們看起來不一樣、我們穿得不一樣、我們的語言不一樣。但是不一樣不是件壞事，被誤解不是件壞事。當你擁有天才的時候，大家不會懂你想做的事。如果你能站穩立場、自在做自己，其他都不重要<ref name="ysolife"/>。」

== 單曲 ==
《[[加把勁_(蕾哈娜歌曲)|加把勁]]》（加拿大歌手[[德雷克_(歌手)|德雷克]]客串）是專輯首波主打單曲，於2016年1月27日、專輯於[[潮汐|Tidal]]發佈的幾小時前發行。蕾哈娜親自在推特上確認此曲為專輯的第一支單曲<ref>{{cite news|url=http://time.com/4195453/rihanna-work-drake-new-song-anti/|title=Here’s Rihanna’s New Song ‘Work’ With Drake|work=[[時代_(雜誌)|Time]]|date=2016-01-27|accessdate=2016-01-27|archive-date=2016-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160204045740/http://time.com/4195453/rihanna-work-drake-new-song-anti/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲首周空降[[美國|美國]][[告示牌百強單曲榜|告示牌百強單曲榜]]第9位，成為她第27支打進前10位的單曲，與[[瑪麗·嘉兒|瑪麗·嘉兒]]、[[珍納·積遜|珍納·積遜]]與[[艾爾頓·約翰|艾爾頓·約翰]]並列為擁有第五多前10位單曲的歌手<ref name="workdebut">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6859557/rihanna-anti-work-billboard-charts?utm_source=twitter|title=Rihanna's 'Anti' & 'Work' Blast Onto Billboard Charts|work=Billboard|last1=Caulfield|first1=Keith|last2=Trust|first2=Gary|date=2016-02-01|accessdate=2016-02-02|archive-date=2016-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160214133634/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6859557/rihanna-anti-work-billboard-charts?utm_source=twitter|dead-url=no}}</ref>。從出道曲《Pon de Replay》到《加把勁》總共用了10年零8個月達成此紀錄，使她成為最快達成此紀錄的個人歌手<ref name="rihannarecord">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6865869/rihanna-ties-mariah-janet-elton-hot-100-top-10s|title=Rihanna Ties Mariah, Janet & Elton for Fifth-Most Hot 100 Top 10s|work=Billboard|last=Trust|first=Gary|date=2016-02-02|accessdate=2016-02-02|archive-date=2016-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160208225543/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6865869/rihanna-ties-mariah-janet-elton-hot-100-top-10s|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲於發行第4周登上告示牌百強單曲榜冠軍位置，成為她於美國第14支冠軍單曲，使她成為繼[[披頭四|披頭四]]（20支）跟瑪麗·嘉兒（18支）後擁有最多美國冠軍單曲的歌手<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6882910/rihanna-drake-no-1-work-hot-100|title=Rihanna & Drake Rise to No. 1 on Hot 100 With 'Work'|work=Billboard|last=Trust|first=Gary|date=2016-02-22|accessdate=2016-02-22|archive-date=2016-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160223045109/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6882910/rihanna-drake-no-1-work-hot-100|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[更好的吻|更好的吻]]》跟《[[需要我|需要我]]》於2016年3月30日分別派往電台作為專輯的第二跟第三支單曲發行。《更好的吻》於告示牌百強單曲榜登上最高第62位，並登上[[告示牌舞曲排行榜|告示牌舞曲排行榜]]冠軍位置，成為她該榜第26支冠軍單曲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7453641/rihanna-26th-no-1-dance-club-songs-chart-kiss-it-better|title=Rihanna Gets Her 26th No. 1 on Dance Club Songs Chart With 'Kiss It Better'|work=Billboard|author=Gordon Murray|date=2016-07-28|accessdate=2016-02-22|archive-date=2016-09-26|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6ko2r2DWH?url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7453641/rihanna-26th-no-1-dance-club-songs-chart-kiss-it-better|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《需要我》於告示牌百強單曲榜登上最高第7位，成為其第29支前10位單曲，使她成為擁有第三多前10位單曲的歌手<ref>{{cite news|last1=Trust|first1=Gary|title=Justin Timberlake Debuts at No. 1 on Hot 100 With 'Can't Stop the Feeling!'|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7370592/justin-timberlake-debuts-no-1-hot-100-cant-stop-the-feeling|work=Billboard|date=2016-05-16|accessdate=2016-07-22|archive-date=2017-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171219174441/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7370592/justin-timberlake-debuts-no-1-hot-100-cant-stop-the-feeling|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲同時打破《[[找到愛|找到愛]]》在榜週數達41週的紀錄，成為她在榜週數最長的單曲<ref>{{cite web |author=Gary Trust |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7588020/rihanna-needed-me-longest-charting-hit-hot-100-chart-moves |title=Rihanna's 'Needed Me' Is Her Longest-Charting Hit: Hot 100 Chart Moves |publisher=Billboard |date=2016-11-23 |accessdate=2016-12-18 |archive-date=2016-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161203042149/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7588020/rihanna-needed-me-longest-charting-hit-hot-100-chart-moves |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《[[無法忘懷的愛|無法忘懷的愛]]》於2016年9月27日成為專輯第四支單曲發行。歌曲首周空降美國告示牌藍調/嘻哈單曲榜第30位以及百強單曲榜第83位<ref>{{cite news|last1=Mendizabal|first1=Amaya|title=Guordan Banks' 'Keep You In Mind' Reaches No. 1 on Adult R&B Songs|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7393407/guordan-banks-adult-rb-songs|accessdate=2016-08-24|work=Billboard|date=2016-06-06|archive-date=2016-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160808214301/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7393407/guordan-banks-adult-rb-songs|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲其後於告示牌百強單曲榜最高登上第5位，成為專輯第3支打進前10位的單曲，也是其本人第30支前10位單曲<ref>{{cite news|author=Gary Trust|title=Rihanna Earns Landmark 30th Top 10 Hit on Billboard Hot 100 Chart|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7694353/hot-100-rihanna-love-on-the-brain-30-top-ten-hits|accessdate=2017-02-28|work=Billboard|date=2017-02-21|archive-date=2017-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170303042638/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7694353/hot-100-rihanna-love-on-the-brain-30-top-ten-hits|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

